## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Adapter choice for demo**: The plan creates all 3 adapters (CSV, SAP Mock, Odoo Mock). During demo, which should be the **default startup adapter**? Options:
> - **CSV** (current behaviour, zero risk) — switch to SAP mock via the UI toggle
> - **SAP Mock** (more impressive for judges) — shows SAP document numbers immediately

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Write-back scope**: Should the Orchestrator automatically push production orders after every agent run, or should it require explicit HITL approval first? The plan currently auto-pushes with an audit trail, but we can add a "staging" mode where orders are queued for human review before ERP push.

